      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Processes jobs one by one but if we receive 504 We add\nanother job where it will retry and get the\n\n\nOn 504 pause the queue for 3s and resume it later\n\n\nWith the help of perfromance from perf_hooks\nwe can calculate the execution time of the job and delay the \njob processing to not have the execution time of \njob processing below 1 second",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Processes jobs one by one but if we receive 504 We add\nanother job where it will retry and get the\n\n\nOn 504 pause the queue for 3s and resume it later\n\n\nWith the help of perfromance from perf_hooks\nwe can calculate the execution time of the job and delay the \njob processing to not have the execution time of \njob processing below 1 second",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 487
    },
